btn" href="https://itch.io/jam/ssjidle/rate/2126167"><svg stroke-linejoin="round" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" role="img" stroke-width="2" class="svgicon icon_award" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden version="1.1"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"></circle><polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88"></polyline></svg>Submission to Summer Slow Jams 2023: Idle</a></li></ul><script type="text/javascript">new I.GameUserTools('#user_tools')</script><div id="wrapper" class="main wrapper"><div id="inner_column" class="inner_column size_very_large family_neucha"><div id="header" class="header has_image align_center"><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyNTkwMTkyLmpwZw==/original/2ZVd%2FJ.jpg" alt="REEL"/><h1 itemprop="name" class="game_title">REEL</h1></div><div id="view_html_game_9295739" class="view_html_game_page view_game_page page_widget base_widget buy_on_top ready"><div id="html_embed_8811106" class="html_embed_widget base_widget embed_wrapper"><div data-height="584" data-width="960" class="game_frame game_pending" style="width: 960px; height: 584px"><div class="iframe_placeholder" data-iframe="&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://v6p9d9t4.ssl.hwcdn.net/html/8195105/REEL_ver.1.0.1_webGL/index.html&quot; allowtransparency=&quot;true&quot; webkitallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; mozallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; msallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; id=&quot;game_drop&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allow=&quot;autoplay; fullscreen *; geolocation; microphone; camera; midi; monetization; xr-spatial-tracking; gamepad; gyroscope; accelerometer; xr; cross-origin-isolated&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;"><button class="button load_iframe_btn"><svg stroke-linejoin="round" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" role="img" stroke-width="2" class="svgicon icon_play" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden version="1.1"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg> Run game</button></div></div></div><div class="donate"><a href="https://luhdurr.itch.io/reel/purchase" class="button donate_btn" data-donate="false">Download Now</a></div><div class="columns"><div class="left_col column"><div class="formatted_description user_formatted"><p>Discover strange fish on a distant alien planet in <em>REEL</em>, a 2d idle game made by a team of four.&nbsp;</p>  <p>Visit the shack, upgrade equipment, and read more about your findings as you spend the night on a mysterious dock. With various creatures, scenes, and endings to unlock, this unfamiliar world will soon be your home.<br><em><br>‧˚₊꒷꒦︶︶︶꒷꒦︶︶︶꒦꒷‧₊˚⊹</em></p>  <p>This game was created for the <a href="https://itch.io/jam/ssjidle" target="_blank" style="font-size: inherit">PIGSquad</a> 2023 Idle Slow Jam with a theme of &quot;Mutation.&quot;&nbsp;</p>  <p>It was a two-week long project full of all-nighters, Unity being Unity, and Gartic Phone on Discord. Our team members each had their main roles, but we often crossed paths and collaborated on different parts to create the final game. This is our baby, and we hope you enjoy it!</p>  <p>(Playable in browser, but we recommend downloading the game since browser performance may vary.)<br><strong><br></strong></p>  <p><strong>Adam Doolittle</strong>: UI/UX<br></p>  <ul><li><a href="http://adamisaiahdoolittle.dev" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Website</a></li><li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adam-doolittle-04bbab251/" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">LinkedIn</a></li><li><a href="https://www.artstation.com/adamdoolittle" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">ArtStation</a></li></ul>  <p><strong>Anthony</strong> <strong>Cerullo</strong>: Art</p>  <ul><li><a href="https://anthonycerullo.carrd.co/" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Website</a></li><li><a href="https://twitter.com/squid1nks" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Twitter</a></li></ul>  <p><strong>Reii</strong>: Programming</p>  <ul><li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/4.00am_sketchbooks/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Instagram<br></a></li><li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/4.00am_sketchbooks/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener"></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Youtube</a></li></ul>  <p><strong>Ryna (neurophonic)</strong>: Music &amp; SFX</p>  <ul><li><a href="https://soundcloud.com/neurophonic" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">SoundCloud</a>&nbsp;(Reel OST <a href="https://soundcloud.com/neurophonic/sets/reel-ost" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Playlist</a>)</li></ul></div><div class="more_information_toggle"><div class="toggle_row"><a class="toggle_info_btn" href="javascript:void(0)">More information<svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_down_tick" height="6" width="12" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 37 20"><path d="m2.0858 0c-1.1535 0-2.0858 0.86469-2.0858 1.9331 0 0.5139 0.21354 1.0183 0.38704 1.1881l18.113 16.879 18.112-16.879c0.174-0.1696 0.388-0.674 0.388-1.1879 0-1.0684-0.932-1.9331-2.086-1.9331-0.577 0-1.111 0.23008-1.49 0.57992l-14.924 13.894-14.925-13.893c-0.3777-0.34998-0.9134-0.581-1.4902-0.581z"/></svg></a></div><div class="info_panel_wrapper"><div id="game_info_panel_1679069" class="game_info_panel_widget base_widget"><table><tbody><tr><td>Updated</td><td><abbr title="29 June 2023 @ 11:47"><span aria-hidden="true" class="icon icon-stopwatch"></span> 22 hours ago</abbr></td></tr><tr><td>Published</td><td><abbr title="27 June 2023 @ 06:41"><span aria-hidden="true" class="icon icon-stopwatch"></span> 3 days ago</abbr></td></tr><tr><td>Status</td><td><a href="https://itch.io/games/released">Released</a></td></tr><tr><td>Platforms</td